comments:
> How are you accessing it?

My editor, and also its user plug-ins, maintain dynamic nodes for specific view
preferenes, depending on what's opened in this editor.  It's all public APIs:

// get base node (preferences contributed via plugin.xml)
IPreferenceNode baseNode = PlatformUI.getWorkbench().getPreferenceManager()
                                     .find(LPEX_BASE_PREFERENCE_PAGE);

// and then add node(s)
baseNode.add(...);
// and remove node(s)
baseNode.remove(...);
